      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously sorted E92 M3, a true high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist. This S65 V8 power plant has been maintained to aerospace standards, with the critical rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements already proactively completed using high-tolerance VAC Motorsports components. The DCT dual-clutch transmission features an updated GTS software flash for crisper downshift rev-matching and lightning-fast engagement. Zero subframe deflection and a pristine underside reflect a life spent in a climate-controlled environment. The paintwork retains incredible depth and clarity, protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating that highlights the aggressive flared arches. This is a turn-key, apex-ready machine with linear power delivery and a chassis balance that modern electronic steering simply cannot replicate. No leaks, no codes, just pure atmospheric induction.",
